description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Kitten in a basket full of flowers
-White kitten on porch
-Cherry blossoms and a white cat
-Two kittens wrapped in sheets
-Fluffy kitten cuddling in a flower pot
-Easter eggs and a little kitten
-Cat sniffing pink flowers
-Beautiful wildflowers and a cat
-Kitten and colorful flowers
-Three kittens in a basket
name: Cat Canvas
